Effect: Learn three Moves from the list below at the Rank of Enhanced Embrace you are taking or lower. Moves marked with an Embrace require that Embrace to be chosen.
Rank 1: Defend Order (None), Fell Needle (Arachnid’s Embrace), Fury Cutter (None), Rage Powder (Monarch’s Embrace), Rolling Fog (None), Struggle Bug (Monarch’s Embrace), Sticky Web (Arachnid’s Embrace)
Rank 2: Attack Order (Arachnid’s Embrace), Heal Order (Monarch's Embrace), Infestation (None), Powder (Monarch’s Embrace), Signal Beam (None), Steamroller (None), Spider Web (Arachnid’s Embrace)
Rank 3: Bug Buzz (None), Leech Life (Arachnid’s Embrace), Lunge (None), Megahorn (None), Pollen Puff (Monarch’s Embrace), Quiver Dance (Monarch’s Embrace), Skitter Smack (Arachnid’s Embrace)
